import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";
import "./App.css";
import SnackOrBoozeApi from "./Api";
import { Card, CardBody, CardTitle, CardText } from "reactstrap";

function AddItem() {
    return <>
       
       <section>
      <Card>
        <CardBody>
          <CardTitle className="font-weight-bold text-center">
           AddItem
          </CardTitle>
          <form>
            <label htmlFor="name">
                Name
                <input type="text" />   
            </label>
            
          </form>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    </section>
    </>
}
 export default AddItem;
